Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the conclusion I had reached
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,after 16 years on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncomplicated friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncomplicated classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that the new school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,year was going swimmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to hope we get\Nan uncomplicated homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's saying something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be some kind of curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's covered in blood, and she's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our homeroom teacher for this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hiyori Hiwamura, our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the first day of the new semester,\Npeople started saying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you offend her, she'll curse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Students are so scared of her that she's ended up\Nwith the moniker, "Spooky Scary Sensei".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Spooky Scary Sensei's notebook,\Nand it had a bunch of talismans stuck in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She tackled me to the ground all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She muttered a curse at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, there were all sorts of testimonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe someone that creepy\Nis our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Spooky Scary Sensei, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing in there all on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's start the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But school's finished for the day.\NThere aren't any students here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she using plushies to represent\Nthe students in some kind of cursed ritual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just like everyone said, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we'll review\Nwhat you learned in first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Opinion."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone tell me what this word means?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Cuttlefish-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuttlefish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It means, someone's own impression of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! Th-That's correct! Gold star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's playing both roles herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next question!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe she really is just practicing\Nhow to teach a class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With plushies as students!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Pufferfish-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the air or mood around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, her voice is way too shaky and quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose my voice is too quiet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she realized!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a breath deep enough to expand your stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll be able to speak more strongly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she strip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was she trying to make it easier\Nto see her stomach expanding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you can understand\Nwithout taking your clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That breathing method's for giving birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, she has no stamina at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, like, wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so weak and wimpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look away... for various reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's take a break for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That chair there... She moved it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,get really bad stage fright and have no stamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was finally able to fulfill my dream\Nof becoming a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though it's only my first year doing\Nthis, I was able to become a homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought I need to do my best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Her voice is getting quieter and quieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning I tripped and hit my head\Non the door and it made a big noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so I ended up scaring everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's why she had blood on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to check what's next\Non the schedule so I don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not talismans! They're sticky notes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The tackle...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sowwy asdfg hjkl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've solved the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of my class isn't a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice is unsteady, and she has no stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's a hard worker...\Nshe's more like a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I'm gonna head off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... abik ghjkl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, could you say that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Abikura-kun, thank you for helping me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell for her hook, line, and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that encounter, I can't help worrying\Nabout that strange teacher of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three... One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiwamura-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she trying to do some training\Nso that she can build up her stamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, what's up with that tracksuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so tight on her! It's gotta be\Nfrom when she was in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already tired\Nafter finishing the warmup exercises!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! Time to start today's special training!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Special training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump rope?! I see, jump rope is so easy that even
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak and Wimpy Sensei should\Nbe able to do it without overexerting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who can't even manage\Nto jump the rope at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's acting like she finished a whole set...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll trip if she tries to walk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Asd fgh! Abikura-kun! It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At this school, they hold\Na big jump rope tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,between all the classes\Nevery sports day in October, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I have a lot less stamina\Nthan the average person,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to practice for it\Nso I don't let everyone down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's only April right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I think you'd be better off\Nsticking with basic exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like doing strength training at home\Nor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but it didn't exactly... go to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, when I exert myself,\NI end up making strange noises,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was worried about disturbing my neighbors...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange noises?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the ones people thought were curses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dfsdfm asfxp weofl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd be willing to help me, Abikura-kun,\NI think I might be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How did things end up like this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... I can't stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, make small talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sensei. What's your ideal type?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I just ask her that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone known to dress smartly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who has a strong voice and good leadership skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who the students can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the type of teacher I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought I was talking about teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, like, that's the exact opposite\Nof how she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was what she meant by strange noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Weak and Wimpy Sensei,\Neven her motor coordination is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone thinks of our homeroom teacher as Spooky\NScary Sensei, but it's just a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Spooky... I mean, Hiwamura-sensei.\NYou dropped one of your notebooks-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's just trying to\Nremember everyone's names,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but does she have to treat it\Nlike kanji practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been doing her best, but she's so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do to help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiwamura-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crying so much. What is she reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The author's bio?! What on earth did they write?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Weak and Wimpy Sensei,\Nshe even has weak tear ducts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it made her cry that much,\NI'm kinda intrigued as to what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the kind of books she's buying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm the one on the verge of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she not have enough money or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Weak and Wimpy Sensei,\Nshe's no good at budgeting, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness. She had enough after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need a bag? They're five yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so close that she doesn't\Nhave five yen left over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She would not, in fact, be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at the best of times, Weak and Wimpy Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,would struggle to get home safely\Nwhile carrying three books and an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiwamura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Abikura-kun?! Asdfg hjkl...I'm sowwy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry, ah, I mean... Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, please use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A bag? Oh gosh, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it's so flimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I figured it'd be better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The bag you gave me protected\Nmy books just in time, Abikura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My clothes ended up getting wet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I like books. Thank you for protecting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Her shirt's gone all see-through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, you should probably keep your jacket on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Weak and Wimpy Sensei,\Neven her luck is lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiwamura-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Abikura-kun, good... mornngh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Why're you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a morning person,\Nso I overslept by accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Weak and Wimpy Sensei,\Nshe can't even wake up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's second period is my\Nfirst long homeroom with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I need to get there early\Nso I can get ready properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful... or rather, um your shirt button...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! G-Goo mornngh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she really be able to manage\Nan entire hour-long homeroom session?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's enough of a mess in our normal\Nshort homeroom time every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay everyone, the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,has come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What, our time has come?! Is that a threat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Another homeroom session that's dead on arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't even make it one second in.\NEveryone's totally freaked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her handwriting's all shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she even more nervous than usual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she writing?! Sutras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the start of our own funeral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone totally off the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face looks pretty red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she still recovering from running this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Spooky Scary Sensei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...holding a box cutter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she charging up for an attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing chalk is too tame for\NSpooky Scary Sensei! She throws box cutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, she can't throw anything\Nwith her noodle arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some reason\Nshe's stuck on the floor like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first long homeroom with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll be the class president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's our first long homeroom\Nsession of the new school year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that means we need to decide\Non our class president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll take it from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man, this isn't simple at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Abikura-kun, um, could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,help me get free?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tights are caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not wearing panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I overslept this morning...\NI forgot to put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you forget THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I can understand after seeing\Nhow flustered she was this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I've got a cramp in my leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't just grab her tights\Nin front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Abikura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want my first long homeroom session\Nwith everyone to end in failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure, I'll untangle it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll now continue this homeroom session!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Prez! Will ya do my homework for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do it to help Sensei,\Nbut becoming class president was a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The simple school life I envisioned\Nis crumbling right before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kinda death threat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To Abikura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak with you\Nabout class operations going forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so would you be able to stay behind after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Time with Sensei, just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess being class president\Nisn't so bad after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Abikura-kun, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A megaphone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, Sensei, I thought we were supposed to be\Ndiscussing class operations?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was my intention,\Nbut at the staff meeting today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiwamura-sensei,\Nyour voice is quite difficult to hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't it hinder your ability to teach class?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right on the money, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, if I use this,\Neveryone should be able to hear me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Asd fgh jkl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's putting a lot of effort into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's still inaudible,\Neven with the megaphone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like people are only scared of you because\Nthey don't know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They're scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! She hadn't noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The students are scared of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I feel bad for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had noticed that nobody\Nwas willing to look me in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, you interact with me just fine,\Ndon't you, Abikura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Abikura-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you weren't a particularly\Nassertive student in your first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite that, you wanted\Nto volunteer for class president,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's how you mustered up\Nthe courage to speak to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impressive! I really respect that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, she's getting the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think using a megaphone is a great idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe just try to speak a little slower\Nand make sure you enunciate clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then let's check if you can\Nhear me from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if I stand at the podium up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Piper picked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you! Loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This way people won't be\Nscared of me anymore, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think my feelings will reach everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They will! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Abikura-kun! Are my feelings reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we in a soap opera or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always helping me out,\Naren't you, Abikura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, shucks, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happen to be around\Nwhen she's working hard to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I really might like Sensei, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, this still tires me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The megaphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The precious item that's gonna help\NSensei connect with everyone in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, Abikura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm sorry, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll move right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say anything right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't manage to discuss class\Noperations much in the end, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll just try again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Abikura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live your dream of being class president!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, she totally got the wrong idea about me.
